Package com.tangosol.util

Class SafeSortedMap.SubMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
com.tangosol.util.SafeSortedMap.SubMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - key type
V - value type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, ConcurrentMap<K,V>, ConcurrentNavigableMap<K,V>, Map<K,V>, NavigableMap<K,V>, SortedMap<K,V>
Enclosing class:
SafeSortedMap<K,V>
protected static class SafeSortedMap.SubMap<K,V> extends AbstractMap<K,V> implements ConcurrentNavigableMap<K,V>, Cloneable, Serializable
SubMap delegation to manage SafeSortedMap.NULL in entry key and/or value.
